  "original_title": "\u0b85\u0bae\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bb2\u0bbe\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bca\u0b9f\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bca\u0b9f\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0b9a\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bc2\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1 \u0b9a\u0bae\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bb5\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd ; \u0b87\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bb2\u0bbf !",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Shooting incidents continue in Ambalangoda; Two victims!",
      "author": "",
      "body_lines": [
        "Ambalangoda police have said that two people have died in the shooting that took place in Kalakoda Velaparai area of \u200b\u200bAmbalangoda this night (27).",
        "According to the police, a 49-year-old man named Vijith D Soyza from Kalakoda area of \u200b\u200bAmbalangoda and a 45-year-old man named Ajith Sudarshana from the same area have died.",
        "Meanwhile, it is noted that a thirty-five-year-old father of three children died in the shooting that took place yesterday (26) afternoon in Uravatta area of \u200b\u200bAmbalangodai."
      ],
